1
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:54,580
=Eight Hundred=

2
00:01:59,580 --> 00:02:04,980
(A week ago)

3
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:23,100
I found the person you were looking for.

4
00:02:26,790 --> 00:02:27,630
Who is it?

5
00:02:28,550 --> 00:02:29,790
Chen Hui didn't tell me.

6
00:02:30,900 --> 00:02:33,180
He told you to go
to the Photo Studio to find him at 1 PM.

7
00:02:44,500 --> 00:02:48,340
(Shiguang Photo Studio)

8
00:02:49,700 --> 00:02:50,540
It's a deal.

9
00:02:51,070 --> 00:02:52,230
I'll give you a discount.

10
00:02:52,230 --> 00:02:53,270
When we're done,

11
00:02:53,270 --> 00:02:54,790
I'll put the photos in the window

12
00:02:54,790 --> 00:02:55,630
as a display.

13
00:02:55,860 --> 00:02:56,700
No problem.

14
00:02:56,700 --> 00:02:57,830
Alright, I'll get back to work then.

15
00:02:57,830 --> 00:02:58,670
Sure thing.

16
00:03:02,260 --> 00:03:03,110
It's okay.

17
00:03:03,110 --> 00:03:04,110
Go change your clothes.

18
00:03:04,700 --> 00:03:05,830
Like I said,

19
00:03:05,830 --> 00:03:06,830
let's just

20
00:03:06,830 --> 00:03:08,390
have a happy photo shoot today.

21
00:03:34,540 --> 00:03:37,500
(Shiguang Photo Studio)

22
00:04:37,470 --> 00:04:38,620
Did you find out who it is?

23
00:04:39,420 --> 00:04:40,550
I did.

24
00:04:40,550 --> 00:04:41,390
I'll take you there.

25
00:04:45,590 --> 00:04:47,260
I haven't met the person either.

26
00:04:47,260 --> 00:04:48,940
I have to pick them out for you.

27
00:04:48,940 --> 00:04:51,900
Otherwise, you might get the wrong person
and say I'm lying to you again.

28
00:05:09,060 --> 00:05:11,110
Where did Hui go?

29
00:05:11,110 --> 00:05:12,180
Why isn't he back yet?

30
00:05:12,180 --> 00:05:13,310
I'll go out and look for him.

31
00:05:13,990 --> 00:05:14,830
Wait...

32
00:05:35,740 --> 00:05:36,710
Which way?

33
00:05:36,710 --> 00:05:37,740
Up the mountain ahead.

34
00:05:40,030 --> 00:05:41,470
Where exactly are we going?

35
00:05:41,470 --> 00:05:42,910
You'll know when we get there.

36
00:06:29,350 --> 00:06:30,670
(Dialing)
The road is ending soon.

37
00:06:30,670 --> 00:06:31,740
Where exactly are we going?

38
00:06:32,670 --> 00:06:34,150
We're almost there. Just ahead.

39
00:06:35,030 --> 00:06:36,910
Listen, don't you dare trick me.

40
00:06:37,620 --> 00:06:38,820
I'll burn you alive if you do.

41
00:06:38,820 --> 00:06:40,100
(Dialing)

42
00:06:40,490 --> 00:06:43,030
Limin, Huo Kaiming wants me
to hand Cai over to him,

43
00:06:43,030 --> 00:06:44,260
or he's going to burn me alive!

44
00:07:25,660 --> 00:07:29,580
=Episode 9=
(Rainbow Glow)

45
00:07:30,300 --> 00:07:31,620
(Yingxiong Roller Skating Rink)

46
00:07:31,620 --> 00:07:33,260
Songge, the soda is here.

47
00:07:33,260 --> 00:07:34,420
(Yingxiong Roller Skating Rink.
Get Active)

48
00:07:34,420 --> 00:07:35,260
Songge.

49
00:07:37,590 --> 00:07:38,430
Mr. Hu.

50
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,150
Could you come over and help me out?

51
00:07:41,150 --> 00:07:42,000
What happened?

52
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:43,700
You'll see when you get here. Let's go.

53
00:07:46,550 --> 00:07:47,390
Mr. Hu,

54
00:07:47,990 --> 00:07:49,710
could you watch Chen Hui for a bit?

55
00:07:49,710 --> 00:07:51,380
I have some
urgent business to attend to.

56
00:07:51,380 --> 00:07:53,110
I still have deliveries
to make in the countryside.

57
00:07:53,790 --> 00:07:54,910
It'll only be half an hour.

58
00:07:55,110 --> 00:07:56,820
I'll give you an extra 100 yuan.

59
00:07:56,820 --> 00:07:58,320
It's not about the money.

60
00:07:59,260 --> 00:08:00,110
Mr. Hu,

61
00:08:00,110 --> 00:08:01,030
when Chen Hui was well,

62
00:08:01,030 --> 00:08:02,350
he treated you well, didn't he?

63
00:08:02,350 --> 00:08:04,590
Now that he's sick, you're just going
to turn your back on him?

64
00:08:04,590 --> 00:08:06,180
Songge, look at what you're saying.

65
00:08:06,180 --> 00:08:07,020
Fine.

66
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:08,180
Go on now.

67
00:08:08,180 --> 00:08:09,310
I'll keep an eye on him for you.

68
00:08:09,990 --> 00:08:10,860
Thank you.

69
00:08:10,860 --> 00:08:11,990
I'll be back soon.

70
00:08:17,460 --> 00:08:20,740
(Welcome to Yingxiong)

71
00:08:25,620 --> 00:08:26,550
I was wrong then.

72
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:29,790
I shouldn't have framed Huo Kaiming
for the cough syrup business.

73
00:08:29,790 --> 00:08:31,350
The police will surely find out

74
00:08:31,350 --> 00:08:33,380
that he wasn't the source of the traffic.

75
00:08:33,380 --> 00:08:34,500
Now that I'm sick,

76
00:08:34,500 --> 00:08:35,900
we must keep shipping goods

77
00:08:35,900 --> 00:08:37,780
to divert the police's
suspicion away from us.

78
00:08:38,110 --> 00:08:40,230
But all our downline dealers
have been arrested.

79
00:08:40,230 --> 00:08:41,780
How can we ship anything?

80
00:08:41,780 --> 00:08:43,020
I have a way.

81
00:08:45,620 --> 00:08:46,460
A switch.

82
00:08:56,780 --> 00:09:00,500
(People's Public Security)

83
00:09:15,430 --> 00:09:16,270
Chief Liu.

84
00:09:18,130 --> 00:09:19,820
Are you heading back
to the municipal PSB?

85
00:09:21,140 --> 00:09:23,110
Once the colleagues
from the municipal PSB

86
00:09:23,110 --> 00:09:24,710
finish handing over the evidence,
we'll go together.

87
00:09:24,810 --> 00:09:27,310
Actually, I should have gone
to say goodbye to Mrs. Chen.

88
00:09:27,620 --> 00:09:30,380
But your family has been so busy lately,
I didn't want to trouble you.

89
00:09:30,380 --> 00:09:31,230
That's alright.

90
00:09:32,340 --> 00:09:33,300
So, Chief Liu,

91
00:09:33,300 --> 00:09:34,540
regarding this case,

92
00:09:34,800 --> 00:09:36,700
does the municipal PSB
have any instructions?

93
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:39,460
The next step is to put all our effort
into capturing Huo Kaiming.

94
00:09:40,230 --> 00:09:41,090
Right,

95
00:09:41,090 --> 00:09:42,900
Jiao Yuqin who conned Huo Kaiming,

96
00:09:42,900 --> 00:09:45,220
whose real name is Yu Susu,
has been caught in Yunchuan.

97
00:09:45,220 --> 00:09:47,690
Colleagues from the municipal PSB
are escorting her back now.

98
00:09:48,380 --> 00:09:49,300
Also, Yu Susu's

99
00:09:49,300 --> 00:09:50,920
husband in Yunchuan said

100
00:09:50,920 --> 00:09:52,490
Huo Kaiming once went to their house

101
00:09:52,940 --> 00:09:54,620
and saw a photo of Yu Susu there.

102
00:09:55,470 --> 00:09:56,500
No wonder.

103
00:09:56,730 --> 00:09:58,220
I was wondering how he knew

104
00:09:58,220 --> 00:10:00,220
Yu Susu and Jiao Yuqin
were the same gang.

105
00:10:02,900 --> 00:10:03,740
Director Chen,

106
00:10:04,620 --> 00:10:05,540
this should be

107
00:10:06,140 --> 00:10:07,740
the last case I ever handle.

108
00:10:08,860 --> 00:10:10,260
It's been a pleasure

109
00:10:10,260 --> 00:10:11,100
working with you.

110
00:10:12,580 --> 00:10:13,420
Chief Liu,

111
00:10:14,220 --> 00:10:15,060
look,

112
00:10:15,060 --> 00:10:17,260
who isn't intimidated by difficulties?

113
00:10:18,460 --> 00:10:19,700
As long as we don't back down,

114
00:10:20,420 --> 00:10:22,280
there will always
be chances to work together.

115
00:10:24,180 --> 00:10:25,500
I'll remember that, Director Chen.

116
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,340
Thank you.

117
00:10:28,340 --> 00:10:29,380
Thank you.

118
00:10:38,510 --> 00:10:40,380
Chief Liu, I've finished
recording everything.

119
00:10:40,380 --> 00:10:41,300
We're ready for the handover.

120
00:10:41,300 --> 00:10:42,140
Good.

121
00:10:42,940 --> 00:10:43,780
Wait.

122
00:10:49,660 --> 00:10:50,500
Give me a glove.

123
00:10:59,300 --> 00:11:01,900
Look, there's a glimmer
on the rim of the bottle.

124
00:11:02,460 --> 00:11:03,300
Do you see it?

125
00:11:05,860 --> 00:11:06,700
No, I don't.

126
00:11:07,100 --> 00:11:08,340
You're looking with the light.

127
00:11:08,340 --> 00:11:10,180
Come here. Everyone, come over.

128
00:11:10,180 --> 00:11:11,320
Take a look, Chief Liu.

129
00:11:12,580 --> 00:11:13,700
There is a ring of light.

130
00:11:14,340 --> 00:11:15,500
It's colorful.

131
00:11:15,500 --> 00:11:17,500
Limin, bring the cough syrup

132
00:11:17,500 --> 00:11:18,980
we found in the lottery shop.

133
00:11:18,980 --> 00:11:19,820
Okay.

134
00:11:28,820 --> 00:11:29,980
(Peidun Cough Syrup)

135
00:11:38,520 --> 00:11:40,710
Why don't those three bottles
have the colorful light?

136
00:11:44,020 --> 00:11:44,860
I feel like I've seen

137
00:11:46,260 --> 00:11:48,060
this rainbow glow somewhere before.

138
00:11:48,060 --> 00:11:52,100
(Peidun Cough Syrup)

139
00:11:53,620 --> 00:11:55,340
(Yingxiong Roller Skating Rink)

140
00:12:01,740 --> 00:12:03,220
I heard from Han Ning

141
00:12:03,900 --> 00:12:04,940
that you're going to

142
00:12:04,940 --> 00:12:05,820
sell the lottery shop?

143
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:08,420
I'm afraid my mom won't be getting out.

144
00:12:10,140 --> 00:12:12,500
I was just thinking
of saving some more money for her.

145
00:12:12,850 --> 00:12:15,100
At least she could
live a bit more comfortably inside.

146
00:12:15,980 --> 00:12:17,180
What about you, then?

147
00:12:18,620 --> 00:12:19,460
Songge,

148
00:12:21,100 --> 00:12:22,180
today is the last time

149
00:12:22,180 --> 00:12:23,020
I'll be singing here.

150
00:12:25,420 --> 00:12:26,740
I want to try my luck in Beijing.

151
00:12:28,540 --> 00:12:29,380
Beijing?

152
00:12:29,900 --> 00:12:32,020
How can you go out
and make it on your own?

153
00:12:32,020 --> 00:12:33,620
It's too worrying.

154
00:12:34,460 --> 00:12:36,540
Xin Yu, why don't you just stay

155
00:12:36,540 --> 00:12:38,140
and sing at the skating rink?

156
00:12:38,140 --> 00:12:39,180
My mom

157
00:12:39,740 --> 00:12:41,420
harmed so many miners.

158
00:12:42,060 --> 00:12:43,900
How can I stay in Fengyang?

159
00:12:44,420 --> 00:12:45,260
Right now,

160
00:12:45,980 --> 00:12:47,860
all I have left are my so-called dreams.

161
00:12:58,580 --> 00:12:59,420
Xin Yu,

162
00:13:00,630 --> 00:13:02,140
this is your salary.

163
00:13:02,140 --> 00:13:03,620
It's calculated for the full month.

164
00:13:04,580 --> 00:13:05,700
We can't help you

165
00:13:05,700 --> 00:13:07,140
with anything else.

166
00:13:08,140 --> 00:13:09,020
Take this

167
00:13:09,020 --> 00:13:11,420
as our small investment

168
00:13:11,420 --> 00:13:12,900
in your dream.

169
00:13:13,420 --> 00:13:14,550
Thank you, Songge,

170
00:13:14,900 --> 00:13:16,300
but I can't take this extra money.

171
00:13:16,780 --> 00:13:18,460
You have plenty of your own expenses.

172
00:13:19,020 --> 00:13:19,940
Just take it.

173
00:13:26,420 --> 00:13:27,700
Thank you, Songge.

174
00:13:30,780 --> 00:13:32,860
Among all of us,

175
00:13:32,860 --> 00:13:35,140
you're the first to leave
this 800-meter radius area.

176
00:13:35,470 --> 00:13:36,920
You can turn your back so decisively

177
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:38,110
for the sake of your dream.

178
00:13:38,740 --> 00:13:40,260
I'm sure you will succeed.

179
00:13:42,660 --> 00:13:44,220
Maybe one day,

180
00:13:44,740 --> 00:13:45,980
I'll be famous, who knows?

181
00:13:52,980 --> 00:13:53,820
Songge,

182
00:13:54,340 --> 00:13:55,700
you're a kind-hearted girl.

183
00:13:55,900 --> 00:13:57,990
I believe that your illness
will get better.

184
00:14:03,940 --> 00:14:04,780
Chen Hui,

185
00:14:05,340 --> 00:14:06,820
you'd better get well soon, too.

186
00:14:06,830 --> 00:14:08,810
Songge is still waiting
for you to take care of her.

187
00:14:14,500 --> 00:14:15,460
I'm off.

188
00:14:16,900 --> 00:14:17,860
Keep it up.

189
00:14:35,580 --> 00:14:36,900
What I'm about to sing

190
00:14:37,740 --> 00:14:39,620
is my final song here.

191
00:14:40,820 --> 00:14:42,660
I hope that within
this 800-meter radius area,

192
00:14:42,660 --> 00:14:43,980
every one of you

193
00:14:44,660 --> 00:14:45,700
has the courage

194
00:14:45,700 --> 00:14:47,700
to chase their own dreams

195
00:14:47,700 --> 00:14:49,380
and realize their truest selves.

196
00:14:50,980 --> 00:14:52,210
"Boundless Oceans, Vast Skies,"

197
00:14:52,700 --> 00:14:53,580
this is for you.

198
00:14:59,130 --> 00:15:01,160
♪Today, I♪

199
00:15:02,810 --> 00:15:05,500
♪Watch the snow
drift by in the cold night♪

200
00:15:05,880 --> 00:15:11,060
♪Drifting afar with a chilled heart♪

201
00:15:11,640 --> 00:15:14,560
♪Chasing in the wind and rain♪

202
00:15:14,850 --> 00:15:17,660
♪Unable to distinguish
shadows in the mist♪

203
00:15:17,970 --> 00:15:20,780
♪The wide sea and sky, you and I♪

204
00:15:21,070 --> 00:15:23,900
♪Could we change? (Who isn't changing?)♪

205
00:15:24,560 --> 00:15:30,810
♪Forgive me for being wild
and unfettered my whole life♪

206
00:15:31,590 --> 00:15:37,590
♪I'm also afraid
that one day I might fall♪

207
00:15:37,880 --> 00:15:40,250
♪Forsaking my ideals♪

208
00:15:40,250 --> 00:15:43,280
♪Anyone can do that♪

209
00:15:44,130 --> 00:15:50,320
♪What's there to fear
if one day it's just you and me?♪

210
00:15:51,840 --> 00:15:54,290
♪Forsaking my ideals♪

211
00:15:54,290 --> 00:15:57,400
♪Anyone can do that♪

212
00:15:58,480 --> 00:16:01,490
♪What's there to fear if one day♪

213
00:16:02,660 --> 00:16:06,000
♪It's just you and me?♪

214
00:16:08,300 --> 00:16:09,300
Xin Yu,

215
00:16:09,300 --> 00:16:10,300
keep it up!

216
00:16:10,300 --> 00:16:13,980
Go, Xin Yu!

217
00:16:13,980 --> 00:16:16,140
Xin Yu, you're the best!

218
00:16:16,860 --> 00:16:18,580
Go!

219
00:16:19,580 --> 00:16:24,260
Go!

220
00:16:45,060 --> 00:16:46,940
(Ding Yue Clinic)

221
00:16:46,940 --> 00:16:47,940
It runs on batteries.

222
00:16:48,740 --> 00:16:49,580
Look.

223
00:16:49,580 --> 00:16:50,960
- Open it here?
- Open it.

224
00:16:52,620 --> 00:16:53,820
I should show you how.

225
00:16:54,620 --> 00:16:55,660
No need.

226
00:16:55,660 --> 00:16:57,860
Isn't it just like making a phone call?

227
00:16:57,860 --> 00:16:59,500
Don't break it, okay?

228
00:16:59,500 --> 00:17:00,780
There's only one in the whole station.

229
00:17:00,780 --> 00:17:01,620
It's for official business.

230
00:17:01,630 --> 00:17:02,540
It was just approved.

231
00:17:02,540 --> 00:17:03,780
Come on, how could I break it?

232
00:17:03,780 --> 00:17:04,780
I'm making a call.

233
00:17:04,780 --> 00:17:05,780
What call?

234
00:17:05,780 --> 00:17:06,740
This is public property. Don't...

235
00:17:06,740 --> 00:17:07,700
- Don't use it for personal calls.
- No.

236
00:17:07,700 --> 00:17:09,780
I'll just give you
the money for the bill later.

237
00:17:09,780 --> 00:17:10,620
- What do you mean?
- Hello?

238
00:17:10,620 --> 00:17:12,700
Liu Na, it's Ding Yue.

239
00:17:12,700 --> 00:17:13,700
Mrs. Chen.

240
00:17:14,900 --> 00:17:17,380
Well, Hongbing's police station

241
00:17:17,380 --> 00:17:18,700
issued a phone,

242
00:17:18,700 --> 00:17:20,140
and he told me to try it out.

243
00:17:20,140 --> 00:17:21,740
I don't have many friends,

244
00:17:21,740 --> 00:17:23,020
so I called you.

245
00:17:23,540 --> 00:17:25,340
How have you been lately?

246
00:17:25,340 --> 00:17:26,200
I'm all right.

247
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:27,580
I had a slight fever last night.

248
00:17:28,920 --> 00:17:29,870
Well, then,

249
00:17:29,870 --> 00:17:30,800
did you take medicine?

250
00:17:30,820 --> 00:17:31,900
I did.

251
00:17:31,900 --> 00:17:32,900
I'm much better.

252
00:17:32,900 --> 00:17:34,100
How is Hui doing?

253
00:17:34,100 --> 00:17:35,460
Hui is doing well.

254
00:17:35,460 --> 00:17:36,460
The doctor said

255
00:17:36,460 --> 00:17:38,140
his chances of recovery are quite good.

256
00:17:39,920 --> 00:17:40,920
That's good.

257
00:17:41,420 --> 00:17:43,940
Next time you bring him to the city,
make sure to let me know.

258
00:17:43,940 --> 00:17:45,420
Sure. When we go to the city,

259
00:17:45,420 --> 00:17:47,380
(Cyclophosphamide Tablets)
we'll come visit you.

260
00:17:47,380 --> 00:17:48,500
We'll come see you.

261
00:17:48,500 --> 00:17:49,900
Limin is here. Give me the phone.

262
00:17:49,900 --> 00:17:51,100
I'm not finished.

263
00:17:51,100 --> 00:17:52,460
Limin is here. I have to go.

264
00:17:52,900 --> 00:17:54,140
Chief Liu,

265
00:17:54,140 --> 00:17:56,140
Ding Yue still has things to tell you,

266
00:17:56,140 --> 00:17:57,700
but I have to set off now.

267
00:17:57,700 --> 00:17:59,020
Goodbye, Liu Na.

268
00:18:00,020 --> 00:18:00,860
Chief Liu,

269
00:18:01,180 --> 00:18:02,700
how is the case going?

270
00:18:02,700 --> 00:18:04,900
It's already in the litigation process.

271
00:18:04,900 --> 00:18:07,380
Cai and Yu Susu
are charged with attempted murder.

272
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:09,420
They're likely to get a life sentence.

273
00:18:09,720 --> 00:18:11,740
The evidence that Huo Kaiming
committed murder and burned the body

274
00:18:11,740 --> 00:18:13,100
is solid.

275
00:18:13,100 --> 00:18:14,340
We just need to catch him.

276
00:18:15,220 --> 00:18:17,300
Is there still no news from Tang?

277
00:18:17,300 --> 00:18:19,620
They found a type
of crystal on the bottle

278
00:18:19,620 --> 00:18:21,820
of Peidun Cough Syrup
with the colored light,

279
00:18:21,820 --> 00:18:23,740
but it's not a common chemical.

280
00:18:23,740 --> 00:18:25,180
There's no way to identify it yet.

281
00:18:25,700 --> 00:18:26,620
Just wait and see.

282
00:18:26,980 --> 00:18:27,840
All right, then.

283
00:18:27,860 --> 00:18:28,700
Chief Liu,

284
00:18:29,100 --> 00:18:31,740
you're always welcome
in Fengyang. Goodbye.

285
00:18:31,740 --> 00:18:32,780
Okay, goodbye.

286
00:18:34,780 --> 00:18:35,660
What's wrong, Master?

287
00:18:38,700 --> 00:18:41,300
The light spots
on the cough syrup bottle,

288
00:18:41,300 --> 00:18:43,140
the multicolored ones,

289
00:18:45,060 --> 00:18:46,900
I've definitely seen them somewhere.

290
00:18:48,100 --> 00:18:49,180
I just can't remember.

291
00:18:50,500 --> 00:18:53,380
Master, it's just that there's
too much going on at home.

292
00:18:53,380 --> 00:18:54,300
Once this is over,

293
00:18:54,300 --> 00:18:55,740
I'm sure you'll remember.

294
00:19:00,860 --> 00:19:01,900
What's going on now?

295
00:19:01,900 --> 00:19:03,340
Let's go over and take a look.

296
00:19:06,380 --> 00:19:08,380
Pay up! You're drinking and not paying?

297
00:19:08,920 --> 00:19:10,100
Everyone, come and look at this.

298
00:19:10,100 --> 00:19:11,180
- Hurry up.
- He's not paying for his drink.

299
00:19:11,180 --> 00:19:12,020
Move aside!

300
00:19:13,860 --> 00:19:15,220
What are you doing? Don't move!

301
00:19:15,220 --> 00:19:16,460
He drank something and didn't pay.

302
00:19:16,460 --> 00:19:18,180
- Don't move!
- He won't pay for his drink!

303
00:19:20,740 --> 00:19:22,020
What's happening here?

304
00:19:22,020 --> 00:19:23,140
Call and get him to the hospital.

305
00:19:23,140 --> 00:19:23,980
Step back.

306
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:26,940
Hello, is this the Workers' Hospital?

307
00:19:26,940 --> 00:19:28,540
Someone collapsed
in front of the Electronics Mall.

308
00:19:28,540 --> 00:19:29,380
Come quickly.

309
00:19:33,100 --> 00:19:33,940
Director Tong.

310
00:19:34,180 --> 00:19:35,380
- Hongbing.
- We're back.

311
00:19:36,660 --> 00:19:37,660
Director Tong,

312
00:19:37,660 --> 00:19:39,580
(Fengyang Mine Workers' Hospital Lab Report)
the miner's test results are out.

313
00:19:39,580 --> 00:19:42,020
It says he has a high level
of Kejianin in his body,

314
00:19:42,020 --> 00:19:43,300
which caused a hallucinogenic reaction.

315
00:19:43,300 --> 00:19:44,420
A hallucinogenic reaction?

316
00:19:44,420 --> 00:19:46,860
Didn't we already take down

317
00:19:46,860 --> 00:19:48,650
the Peidun Cough Syrup
distribution network?

318
00:19:49,090 --> 00:19:50,940
Why is the cough syrup appearing again?

319
00:19:50,940 --> 00:19:52,500
This isn't the only case in town.

320
00:19:52,500 --> 00:19:54,380
We tracked these people down
and checked again.

321
00:19:54,380 --> 00:19:55,980
They all claim they're innocent.

322
00:19:55,980 --> 00:19:57,710
They all say they
never bought cough syrup.

323
00:19:57,980 --> 00:19:58,820
After investigating,

324
00:19:59,320 --> 00:20:00,880
it turns out they're telling the truth.

325
00:20:01,500 --> 00:20:02,360
This matter

326
00:20:02,360 --> 00:20:03,380
is a bit strange.

327
00:20:03,380 --> 00:20:05,380
We've arrested so many downline dealers

328
00:20:05,380 --> 00:20:07,100
and so many sellers.

329
00:20:07,100 --> 00:20:08,820
This situation had stopped

330
00:20:08,820 --> 00:20:10,380
for quite some time.

331
00:20:10,380 --> 00:20:11,980
So, how did these people
who suddenly hallucinated

332
00:20:11,980 --> 00:20:13,500
come into contact with the cough syrup?

333
00:20:13,980 --> 00:20:16,220
This opponent is out of the ordinary.

334
00:20:16,620 --> 00:20:18,580
He can pull off

335
00:20:18,580 --> 00:20:19,620
many inexplicable things.

336
00:20:20,020 --> 00:20:20,940
To be honest,

337
00:20:20,940 --> 00:20:23,100
I still haven't figured out

338
00:20:23,100 --> 00:20:24,460
how he's doing this.

339
00:20:34,740 --> 00:20:37,500
Regarding the recent cases
in Fengyang involving

340
00:20:37,500 --> 00:20:38,500
the cough syrup

341
00:20:38,500 --> 00:20:40,660
and the body-burning homicide,

342
00:20:40,660 --> 00:20:42,220
the nature of these crimes is vile,

343
00:20:42,220 --> 00:20:43,860
causing great harm to society.

344
00:20:43,860 --> 00:20:46,260
On behalf of the Fengyang Police Station,

345
00:20:46,260 --> 00:20:48,100
I solemnly promise here...

346
00:20:48,860 --> 00:20:51,100
You haven't even caught
the person in this case yet.

347
00:20:51,580 --> 00:20:52,460
That's enough, Dad.

348
00:20:52,460 --> 00:20:53,340
Just eat your dinner.

349
00:20:53,900 --> 00:20:56,780
We'll bring
the criminal suspects to justice.

350
00:20:56,780 --> 00:20:57,820
Look at this child.

351
00:20:57,820 --> 00:20:59,500
He's not eating or drinking.

352
00:20:59,500 --> 00:21:00,500
This can't go on.

353
00:21:01,280 --> 00:21:02,130
Come on.

354
00:21:02,180 --> 00:21:04,060
Dad, what are you doing?

355
00:21:04,060 --> 00:21:05,180
Let's feed him some porridge.

356
00:21:05,300 --> 00:21:06,260
Fine...

357
00:21:06,940 --> 00:21:08,300
I'll do it. I'll feed him.

358
00:21:08,300 --> 00:21:09,860
He has his own.

359
00:21:09,860 --> 00:21:10,860
Okay.

360
00:21:13,540 --> 00:21:16,100
Hui, please get well soon.

361
00:21:16,100 --> 00:21:16,980
Come, here.

362
00:21:17,000 --> 00:21:17,870
Come.

363
00:21:19,020 --> 00:21:19,860
Blow on it.

364
00:21:20,340 --> 00:21:21,540
You're taking too long.

365
00:21:21,540 --> 00:21:23,060
Let me do it.

366
00:21:23,060 --> 00:21:24,100
See?

367
00:21:24,100 --> 00:21:24,940
Look at that.

368
00:21:25,460 --> 00:21:26,300
I said let me do it,

369
00:21:26,300 --> 00:21:27,140
- but you still fought me for it.
- What happened?

370
00:21:27,140 --> 00:21:28,420
Aren't you just making a mess, Dad?

371
00:21:28,420 --> 00:21:30,140
You've gone and scalded my grandson!

372
00:21:30,140 --> 00:21:30,980
Hurry!

373
00:21:30,980 --> 00:21:32,850
Go get some cold water and a towel.

374
00:21:32,850 --> 00:21:33,700
You sit down.

375
00:21:33,700 --> 00:21:35,300
It's okay, Dad. It's okay.

376
00:21:35,300 --> 00:21:36,440
I'll take care of it for him.

377
00:21:37,220 --> 00:21:38,300
Let me see.

378
00:21:38,700 --> 00:21:39,540
Quickly.

379
00:21:39,940 --> 00:21:40,900
It's red.

380
00:21:40,900 --> 00:21:42,110
It's fine. Just don't touch it.

381
00:21:46,230 --> 00:21:47,430
It doesn't hurt, does it, Hui?

382
00:21:55,180 --> 00:21:56,020
Son,

383
00:21:57,100 --> 00:21:57,940
today,

384
00:21:58,700 --> 00:22:00,140
Mr. Huang's trial starts.

385
00:22:01,580 --> 00:22:02,420
I

386
00:22:02,980 --> 00:22:04,300
have to go to the city.

387
00:22:05,500 --> 00:22:06,820
After lunch,

388
00:22:07,700 --> 00:22:08,860
I'll be back.

389
00:22:09,820 --> 00:22:10,660
Okay?

390
00:22:15,380 --> 00:22:16,460
Before,

391
00:22:18,140 --> 00:22:19,300
I always linked you

392
00:22:19,300 --> 00:22:20,860
to this case.

393
00:22:23,140 --> 00:22:24,820
Maybe because of those things,

394
00:22:27,500 --> 00:22:28,940
it turned you into this.

395
00:22:33,860 --> 00:22:34,940
Do you hate me?

396
00:22:38,020 --> 00:22:39,220
I had no choice.

397
00:22:39,980 --> 00:22:41,460
I am a policeman.

398
00:22:43,660 --> 00:22:44,500
Try to understand me.

399
00:23:13,420 --> 00:23:14,260
Dad.

400
00:23:19,020 --> 00:23:20,380
You can speak?

401
00:23:25,860 --> 00:23:27,500
I knew

402
00:23:27,500 --> 00:23:28,380
you'd get better.

403
00:23:30,500 --> 00:23:31,340
This is great.

404
00:23:31,860 --> 00:23:32,820
My boy,

405
00:23:33,080 --> 00:23:34,370
you've finally recovered.

406
00:23:38,090 --> 00:23:39,030
I knew

407
00:23:39,040 --> 00:23:40,580
you would get better.

408
00:23:41,140 --> 00:23:42,060
Good boy.

409
00:23:42,340 --> 00:23:43,240
Don't cry.

410
00:23:45,100 --> 00:23:46,140
It was my fault.

411
00:23:46,140 --> 00:23:47,300
It was all my fault.

412
00:24:07,940 --> 00:24:10,420
(Radiation hazard.
Do not enter when light is on)

413
00:24:18,660 --> 00:24:19,780
Thank you, Doctor.

414
00:24:19,780 --> 00:24:22,260
(CT Room)

415
00:24:22,420 --> 00:24:23,540
We have to wait two hours

416
00:24:23,540 --> 00:24:24,820
to get the scans.

417
00:24:27,380 --> 00:24:28,420
Hui,

418
00:24:28,420 --> 00:24:30,700
Mr. Huang's trial is today.

419
00:24:30,700 --> 00:24:32,260
I have to go to the court.

420
00:24:32,260 --> 00:24:33,180
Songge

421
00:24:33,180 --> 00:24:35,580
and your mom are with you, okay?

422
00:24:36,660 --> 00:24:37,780
It's fine, Dad.

423
00:24:37,780 --> 00:24:38,820
Go ahead.

424
00:24:39,220 --> 00:24:40,260
Good boy.

425
00:24:41,060 --> 00:24:41,940
Come back early.

426
00:24:41,940 --> 00:24:43,100
Okay, I will.

427
00:24:43,100 --> 00:24:45,060
Thank you.

428
00:24:46,100 --> 00:24:47,220
Hurry up.

429
00:24:47,220 --> 00:24:48,140
Don't worry.

430
00:24:52,980 --> 00:24:54,340
Does the defendant have

431
00:24:54,340 --> 00:24:56,500
any objections to the criminal facts

432
00:24:56,500 --> 00:24:57,660
(Judge, Presiding Judge, Court Clerk)
alleged by the public prosecutor?

433
00:24:58,340 --> 00:24:59,180
No objections.

434
00:24:59,740 --> 00:25:02,620
The case of defendant Huang Liang
for illegal coal mining

435
00:25:02,620 --> 00:25:03,820
is now for sentencing.

436
00:25:03,820 --> 00:25:04,940
The judgment is as follows.

437
00:25:04,940 --> 00:25:06,100
All rise, please.

438
00:25:11,100 --> 00:25:12,340
Defendant Huang Liang

439
00:25:12,340 --> 00:25:14,060
(Jiangbin Municipal People's Court)
mined coal without

440
00:25:14,060 --> 00:25:15,460
obtaining a mining permit.

441
00:25:15,460 --> 00:25:17,820
His actions constitute
the crime of illegal mining.

442
00:25:17,820 --> 00:25:19,780
The charges
by the prosecution are established,

443
00:25:19,780 --> 00:25:21,380
and this court supports them.

444
00:25:21,380 --> 00:25:23,780
(Defendant)
Defendant Huang Liang surrendered himself,

445
00:25:23,780 --> 00:25:26,180
and a lighter or reduced sentence
may be given by law.

446
00:25:26,180 --> 00:25:28,180
In accordance with Articles 343

447
00:25:28,180 --> 00:25:31,420
and 67 of the Criminal Law
of the People's Republic of China,

448
00:25:31,420 --> 00:25:32,780
the judgment is as follows.

449
00:25:32,780 --> 00:25:33,620
Defendant Huang Liang

450
00:25:33,620 --> 00:25:35,100
is guilty of illegal mining

451
00:25:35,100 --> 00:25:37,340
and is sentenced
to three years and six months,

452
00:25:37,340 --> 00:25:39,580
with a fine of 370,000 yuan.

453
00:25:39,580 --> 00:25:40,820
If you disagree with this judgment,

454
00:25:40,820 --> 00:25:43,620
you may, within 10 days from the
second day after receiving the judgment,

455
00:25:43,620 --> 00:25:44,500
file an appeal

456
00:25:44,500 --> 00:25:47,180
through this court or directly
with the Intermediate People's Court.

457
00:25:47,180 --> 00:25:49,020
This trial is adjourned.

458
00:25:49,020 --> 00:25:51,100
Defendant Huang Liang is to be taken back
to the detention center

459
00:25:51,100 --> 00:25:52,260
to remain in custody.

460
00:26:12,540 --> 00:26:19,540
(Jiangbin Municipal People's Court)

461
00:26:27,140 --> 00:26:27,980
Chief Liu.

462
00:26:27,980 --> 00:26:29,260
Director Chen, get in.

463
00:26:29,370 --> 00:26:30,660
Sorry, I'm late.

464
00:26:31,460 --> 00:26:32,620
As soon as I got to the city,

465
00:26:33,220 --> 00:26:34,900
I took Hui to the hospital first,

466
00:26:35,460 --> 00:26:36,700
which delayed me.

467
00:26:36,700 --> 00:26:37,820
What's wrong with Hui now?

468
00:26:38,380 --> 00:26:39,820
It's good news this time.

469
00:26:39,820 --> 00:26:42,060
He can recognize people,
and he can even speak.

470
00:26:42,060 --> 00:26:43,460
Really? That's great.

471
00:26:43,460 --> 00:26:44,300
Isn't it?

472
00:26:44,300 --> 00:26:45,260
This past month,

473
00:26:45,260 --> 00:26:47,260
Ding Yue and I have been worried sick.

474
00:26:48,340 --> 00:26:49,460
Is your wife here?

475
00:26:49,460 --> 00:26:51,340
She's our family's
"Health Commissioner."

476
00:26:51,340 --> 00:26:52,820
How could she not come for this?

477
00:26:52,820 --> 00:26:54,170
She's at the hospital with Songge.

478
00:26:54,700 --> 00:26:55,820
By the way, Chief Liu,

479
00:26:55,820 --> 00:26:56,700
any news on

480
00:26:57,620 --> 00:26:59,180
Huo Kaiming?

481
00:27:00,020 --> 00:27:01,620
Judging by the blood at the scene,

482
00:27:01,620 --> 00:27:03,380
Hui's blow must have wounded him badly.

483
00:27:03,820 --> 00:27:05,340
He likely died in some mountain gully.

484
00:27:06,620 --> 00:27:07,580
Lately,

485
00:27:08,260 --> 00:27:09,620
I've been mulling something over.

486
00:27:10,780 --> 00:27:12,580
It's not exactly new information,

487
00:27:12,580 --> 00:27:13,780
just a line of thinking.

488
00:27:14,460 --> 00:27:15,300
What's that?

489
00:27:15,700 --> 00:27:16,540
Back then,

490
00:27:17,060 --> 00:27:18,580
when Gao Ying's incident happened,

491
00:27:19,140 --> 00:27:21,220
Huo Kaiming was
the safety officer on duty.

492
00:27:21,740 --> 00:27:24,300
At the very least, the method
of burning the body was the same.

493
00:27:24,300 --> 00:27:25,380
I was thinking,

494
00:27:25,380 --> 00:27:26,380
could we...

495
00:27:27,340 --> 00:27:28,200
Director Chen,

496
00:27:28,210 --> 00:27:31,020
regarding the application
to reopen Gao Ying's case,

497
00:27:31,020 --> 00:27:33,380
the municipal PSB says
they need more supporting materials.

498
00:27:33,980 --> 00:27:36,300
I'll have to go back and pull
the original files from back then.

499
00:27:38,140 --> 00:27:39,100
Alright.

500
00:27:39,100 --> 00:27:40,660
I'll wait for progress on your end.

501
00:27:45,300 --> 00:27:46,140
Director Chen,

502
00:27:46,860 --> 00:27:48,300
please don't mind me asking.

503
00:27:48,300 --> 00:27:49,160
Go ahead.

504
00:27:49,160 --> 00:27:50,140
Now that Hui is awake,

505
00:27:50,420 --> 00:27:52,480
and things are going well
between you and your wife,

506
00:27:52,820 --> 00:27:54,060
why bring this matter up again?

507
00:27:57,420 --> 00:27:58,580
Speaking of our relationship,

508
00:27:59,340 --> 00:28:01,220
Ding Yue and Gao Ying

509
00:28:01,220 --> 00:28:02,580
were besties back then.

510
00:28:04,500 --> 00:28:06,500
Even though so many years have passed,

511
00:28:07,340 --> 00:28:09,060
if I don't clear this up,

512
00:28:09,060 --> 00:28:10,660
I'll always feel

513
00:28:10,660 --> 00:28:11,660
like I've failed Gao Ying

514
00:28:12,680 --> 00:28:13,860
and failed myself,

515
00:28:13,860 --> 00:28:15,700
especially being a police officer now.

516
00:28:18,660 --> 00:28:19,540
I understand.

517
00:28:20,940 --> 00:28:22,420
I'll find another way.

518
00:28:22,420 --> 00:28:23,260
Thank you.

519
00:28:30,040 --> 00:28:30,880
Hello?

520
00:28:31,170 --> 00:28:32,020
Tang,

521
00:28:32,020 --> 00:28:32,860
what is it?

522
00:28:33,540 --> 00:28:35,220
It's about the cough syrup,
Director Chen.

523
00:28:35,220 --> 00:28:37,220
We finally identified
the crystals on the bottle.

524
00:28:37,220 --> 00:28:39,380
It's a substance called polyacrylamide.

525
00:28:39,380 --> 00:28:41,540
I've already faxed
all the materials to your station.

526
00:28:42,180 --> 00:28:43,020
Great.

527
00:28:43,840 --> 00:28:44,700
The case

528
00:28:44,700 --> 00:28:45,820
finally has a new lead.

529
00:28:46,420 --> 00:28:47,900
Tang, thank you for your hard work.

530
00:28:48,580 --> 00:28:49,420
Did you find out

531
00:28:49,940 --> 00:28:51,460
what the substance is used for?

532
00:28:52,340 --> 00:28:54,900
Its most common use for civilians
is in water treatment plants,

533
00:28:55,340 --> 00:28:56,620
used for water purification.

534
00:28:56,620 --> 00:28:57,700
A water treatment plant?

535
00:29:00,100 --> 00:29:02,820
The scans show the blood clot in his brain
is already very small.

536
00:29:03,010 --> 00:29:03,950
It's not a major issue.

537
00:29:04,820 --> 00:29:07,340
Next, focus on restoring some movement.

538
00:29:07,350 --> 00:29:09,300
After all, from lying down so long,
some of the muscles

539
00:29:09,300 --> 00:29:10,580
have already atrophied.

540
00:29:10,580 --> 00:29:11,570
He needs to stay active.

541
00:29:11,950 --> 00:29:13,670
Come back for a check-up
if there are problems.

542
00:29:14,580 --> 00:29:16,020
Thank you, Doctor.

543
00:29:16,150 --> 00:29:16,990
Hearing you say that

544
00:29:17,000 --> 00:29:18,060
puts us much more at ease.

545
00:29:18,900 --> 00:29:20,580
Mom, I'm feeling a bit cooped up.

546
00:29:20,580 --> 00:29:21,580
I want to go for a walk.

547
00:29:22,260 --> 00:29:23,340
I'll go with him,

548
00:29:23,340 --> 00:29:24,180
Mrs. Chen.

549
00:29:24,780 --> 00:29:26,860
- Alright, take good care of him.
- Will do.

550
00:29:26,860 --> 00:29:27,820
Get plenty of exercise.

551
00:29:28,340 --> 00:29:29,460
Careful, Hui.

552
00:29:29,460 --> 00:29:30,300
I'm fine.

553
00:29:30,980 --> 00:29:31,820
Easy.

554
00:29:32,820 --> 00:29:33,940
You two be careful.

555
00:29:33,940 --> 00:29:34,780
Got it, Mrs. Chen.

556
00:29:35,380 --> 00:29:36,620
(Management Promotes
Quality and Standards)

557
00:29:36,630 --> 00:29:38,100
How could you just say you were fine?

558
00:29:38,500 --> 00:29:40,100
You didn't even tell me in advance.

559
00:29:40,100 --> 00:29:41,040
You scared me to death.

560
00:29:42,620 --> 00:29:44,580
Every day I watched
my dad working so hard,

561
00:29:44,580 --> 00:29:46,020
worrying until his hair turned white.

562
00:29:46,500 --> 00:29:48,220
I really couldn't bear
to keep pretending.

563
00:29:49,620 --> 00:29:50,980
This matter is finally over.

564
00:29:51,420 --> 00:29:52,540
It's a relief.

565
00:29:53,340 --> 00:29:54,180
No.

566
00:29:55,180 --> 00:29:56,900
We can't completely
let our guard down yet.

567
00:29:57,500 --> 00:29:58,340
Why?

568
00:29:59,260 --> 00:30:01,820
To be honest, whether it's Lu Yuan,
Xin Yu, or Huo Kaiming,

569
00:30:02,900 --> 00:30:04,580
I've never been afraid of them.

570
00:30:05,180 --> 00:30:06,540
But there is one person

571
00:30:06,540 --> 00:30:07,500
I can never win against.

572
00:30:08,180 --> 00:30:09,020
Who?

573
00:30:09,860 --> 00:30:11,140
- My dad.
- Hui.

574
00:30:12,580 --> 00:30:13,940
The medicine is all picked up.

575
00:30:13,940 --> 00:30:15,100
In two weeks,

576
00:30:15,100 --> 00:30:16,300
just come back for a check-up.

577
00:30:16,910 --> 00:30:17,940
- Okay.
- I'll take this.

578
00:30:17,940 --> 00:30:20,580
Let's go home, and I will cook
something delicious for you.

579
00:30:20,800 --> 00:30:21,660
Okay.

580
00:30:21,660 --> 00:30:22,620
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

581
00:30:23,140 --> 00:30:24,620
The sun is really nice today.

582
00:30:30,860 --> 00:30:31,700
Look at that.

583
00:30:32,460 --> 00:30:33,940
- Dad.
- He's waiting at the door.

584
00:30:34,050 --> 00:30:34,930
Look.

585
00:30:34,940 --> 00:30:36,360
My eldest grandson, you're back.

586
00:30:36,740 --> 00:30:37,740
I

587
00:30:38,260 --> 00:30:40,020
have been worrying about you.

588
00:30:40,500 --> 00:30:41,420
Who is he?

589
00:30:42,580 --> 00:30:43,900
You don't know who he is,

590
00:30:43,900 --> 00:30:45,460
- I'm your grandpa.
- Hui?

591
00:30:45,460 --> 00:30:47,340
You don't even recognize your grandpa?

592
00:30:47,340 --> 00:30:48,260
Hui,

593
00:30:48,260 --> 00:30:49,260
look closely.

594
00:30:49,260 --> 00:30:50,100
This is Grandpa.

595
00:30:50,740 --> 00:30:52,660
You don't even recognize
your grandpa anymore?

596
00:30:52,950 --> 00:30:53,790
This...

597
00:30:54,340 --> 00:30:55,660
How could it turn out like this?

598
00:30:56,540 --> 00:30:57,500
Didn't the doctor check

599
00:30:57,500 --> 00:30:58,900
and say everything was fine?

600
00:30:58,900 --> 00:30:59,860
How about this?

601
00:30:59,860 --> 00:31:00,820
Let's go back to the hospital
for a check-up.

602
00:31:00,820 --> 00:31:02,740
- No, we're not going back.
- Let's go.

603
00:31:02,740 --> 00:31:03,860
Come on, let's go.

604
00:31:03,860 --> 00:31:04,860
We're not going.

605
00:31:04,860 --> 00:31:06,180
I was just joking.

606
00:31:06,180 --> 00:31:07,700
How could I not recognize my grandpa?

607
00:31:07,700 --> 00:31:09,220
You really scared me.

608
00:31:09,220 --> 00:31:10,500
Was it you who burned my hand?

609
00:31:13,220 --> 00:31:14,380
I don't remember that.

610
00:31:14,820 --> 00:31:15,900
But I remember

611
00:31:15,900 --> 00:31:17,060
that you said

612
00:31:17,060 --> 00:31:18,900
you'd go fly kites with me.

613
00:31:20,220 --> 00:31:22,260
- You rascal, you even fooled us.
- Let's go home.

614
00:31:22,260 --> 00:31:23,140
I'm teasing you.

615
00:31:23,140 --> 00:31:23,980
Let's go.

616
00:31:24,660 --> 00:31:25,500
Seriously.

617
00:31:25,500 --> 00:31:27,070
I really thought something was wrong.

618
00:31:31,020 --> 00:31:31,980
- Stick.
- Stick.

619
00:31:31,980 --> 00:31:32,920
- Chicken.
- Chicken.

620
00:31:35,140 --> 00:31:36,880
I told you.

621
00:31:36,890 --> 00:31:38,140
It would've been better to go

622
00:31:38,140 --> 00:31:39,620
to Liusan Mutton Restaurant
and buy some.

623
00:31:39,620 --> 00:31:40,540
You insisted on making it yourself.

624
00:31:40,540 --> 00:31:41,780
Well, after all that work,

625
00:31:41,780 --> 00:31:43,140
it might not even
taste as good as theirs.

626
00:31:43,140 --> 00:31:44,660
What do you know?

627
00:31:44,660 --> 00:31:46,940
The stewed meat outside is so salty.

628
00:31:46,940 --> 00:31:49,020
His nervous system has just recovered,
so can he have that much salt?

629
00:31:49,020 --> 00:31:50,700
Songge can't eat out either.

630
00:31:51,300 --> 00:31:54,500
Besides, the meat I stew
versus the meat from the restaurant,

631
00:31:54,500 --> 00:31:55,780
- how can they be the same?
- Right.

632
00:31:55,780 --> 00:31:56,900
- Isn't that right, Dad?
- It's not the same.

633
00:31:56,900 --> 00:31:58,740
Nothing's as good as your cooking.

634
00:31:58,750 --> 00:32:00,720
- Even Dad said so.
- Home-cooked is always best.

635
00:32:00,740 --> 00:32:01,700
Fine.

636
00:32:01,900 --> 00:32:02,740
You're right.

637
00:32:04,300 --> 00:32:05,140
Come on, man.

638
00:32:05,500 --> 00:32:06,340
Dad,

639
00:32:06,500 --> 00:32:07,420
is this one okay?

640
00:32:08,420 --> 00:32:09,260
This is good.

641
00:32:09,700 --> 00:32:10,820
Hui, do you know?

642
00:32:10,820 --> 00:32:11,660
Your mother,

643
00:32:12,140 --> 00:32:12,980
for your sake,

644
00:32:14,060 --> 00:32:16,140
hasn't had a single night of good sleep.

645
00:32:16,140 --> 00:32:17,700
That you could pull through this time

646
00:32:17,700 --> 00:32:19,180
is all thanks to your mother.

647
00:32:19,180 --> 00:32:20,300
It's been very hard on her.

648
00:32:20,300 --> 00:32:21,260
What can I do?

649
00:32:21,260 --> 00:32:23,340
I've been used to it all my life.

650
00:32:23,340 --> 00:32:24,620
After all, Fengyang

651
00:32:24,620 --> 00:32:25,860
can't do without

652
00:32:25,860 --> 00:32:27,180
your dad.

653
00:32:28,040 --> 00:32:28,900
Don't even say it.

654
00:32:28,900 --> 00:32:30,100
In this family,

655
00:32:30,940 --> 00:32:32,140
if we didn't have your mother,

656
00:32:33,020 --> 00:32:34,100
it'd be even worse.

657
00:32:34,100 --> 00:32:34,940
That's true.

658
00:32:34,940 --> 00:32:36,820
If I don't look after
our family, who will?

659
00:32:37,900 --> 00:32:38,900
I'll do it.

660
00:32:38,900 --> 00:32:39,740
You've got me too.

661
00:32:39,740 --> 00:32:40,720
I'll look after things.

662
00:32:41,980 --> 00:32:42,820
Dad,

663
00:32:42,980 --> 00:32:44,940
you're the best
at looking after everyone.

664
00:32:46,380 --> 00:32:47,220
Indeed.

665
00:32:48,300 --> 00:32:50,100
Songge has been working hard lately too.

666
00:32:50,100 --> 00:32:51,340
Between the roller skating rink

667
00:32:51,340 --> 00:32:53,600
and taking care of Hui,
she's running back and forth.

668
00:32:53,600 --> 00:32:54,540
It's painful to watch.

669
00:32:54,540 --> 00:32:55,700
I'm fine.

670
00:32:55,700 --> 00:32:56,550
Mrs. Chen,

671
00:32:56,560 --> 00:32:59,300
lately, you and Mr. Chen
have been much more tired than I am.

672
00:32:59,300 --> 00:33:01,110
I can see you both
are starting to get white hair.

673
00:33:01,380 --> 00:33:03,780
Besides, I've been in this family
for so many years,

674
00:33:03,780 --> 00:33:05,710
and you've always
been the ones taking care of me.

675
00:33:05,780 --> 00:33:06,900
The things I do

676
00:33:06,900 --> 00:33:07,740
aren't much at all.

677
00:33:08,180 --> 00:33:09,020
Songge,

678
00:33:09,700 --> 00:33:11,020
we are all one family.

679
00:33:11,480 --> 00:33:12,500
Let's not talk about that.

680
00:33:15,020 --> 00:33:17,580
Dad, your grandson is back today.

681
00:33:17,580 --> 00:33:18,820
Even though you're happy,

682
00:33:18,820 --> 00:33:20,500
the rules cannot be broken.

683
00:33:20,500 --> 00:33:21,340
Only half a glass.

684
00:33:22,780 --> 00:33:23,620
Half a glass.

685
00:33:25,580 --> 00:33:26,740
That's enough.

686
00:33:27,300 --> 00:33:29,020
Why did you pour it so full?

687
00:33:29,020 --> 00:33:30,180
Look at this.

688
00:33:31,780 --> 00:33:33,900
This is a waste of good grain.

689
00:33:33,900 --> 00:33:35,540
But this liquor really does smell nice.

690
00:33:41,940 --> 00:33:43,100
Is it good?

691
00:33:43,100 --> 00:33:44,300
Nice. Good.

692
00:33:45,060 --> 00:33:45,900
Come on, Hui.

693
00:33:46,380 --> 00:33:47,220
Yes, Dad.

694
00:33:48,580 --> 00:33:50,500
What kind of father are you?

695
00:33:50,500 --> 00:33:51,860
Hui's just recovered.

696
00:33:51,860 --> 00:33:52,700
Can he even drink?

697
00:33:53,500 --> 00:33:55,540
Right, it's best
to listen to the doctor.

698
00:33:55,540 --> 00:33:56,740
Here, you have a glass.

699
00:34:00,580 --> 00:34:02,420
Mrs. Chen, you drink this juice.

700
00:34:02,420 --> 00:34:03,700
Songge, I'll do it myself.

701
00:34:06,260 --> 00:34:07,100
Alright.

702
00:34:07,340 --> 00:34:08,180
Is everyone ready?

703
00:34:08,180 --> 00:34:09,020
Come on, let's have a toast.

704
00:34:09,020 --> 00:34:10,740
Come on, everyone is here today.

705
00:34:10,740 --> 00:34:12,420
Let's congratulate Hui

706
00:34:12,420 --> 00:34:13,740
on his full recovery.

707
00:34:13,740 --> 00:34:14,580
Shall we?

708
00:34:14,580 --> 00:34:15,720
- Welcome back.
- Thanks, Dad.

709
00:34:16,140 --> 00:34:18,500
I wish you a speedy return to health, Hui.

710
00:34:18,980 --> 00:34:20,540
Thanks, Grandpa. Thanks, Mom.

711
00:34:20,540 --> 00:34:22,180
Dad, I wish you good health too.

712
00:34:22,180 --> 00:34:23,580
Good. Good health to everyone.

713
00:34:23,580 --> 00:34:24,580
Good health to everyone.

714
00:34:25,500 --> 00:34:26,500
Dad, slow down.

715
00:34:27,120 --> 00:34:28,660
Mrs. Chen,
these vegetables are delicious.

716
00:34:28,660 --> 00:34:29,820
- Not too salty?
- No.

717
00:34:29,820 --> 00:34:31,110
- Eat more.
- Alright, will do.

718
00:34:33,420 --> 00:34:34,940
Come on, eat more.

719
00:34:36,860 --> 00:34:37,700
Hui,

720
00:34:38,180 --> 00:34:39,860
now that you're technically recovered,

721
00:34:41,100 --> 00:34:42,820
there's something I need to ask you.

722
00:34:43,780 --> 00:34:44,790
What is it, Dad?

723
00:34:46,140 --> 00:34:47,420
The day of your accident,

724
00:34:48,060 --> 00:34:48,940
what exactly

725
00:34:50,260 --> 00:34:51,660
did Huo Kaiming say to you?

726
00:34:54,900 --> 00:34:55,740
Yes,

727
00:34:59,660 --> 00:35:01,100
what did he say?
